# act configuration for local GitHub Actions simulation
# See: https://github.com/nektos/act

# Use medium-sized Ubuntu image (good balance of compatibility vs size)
# Options: micro, medium, large (large is closest to GitHub but ~18GB)
-P ubuntu-latest=catthehacker/ubuntu:act-latest

# Default to running push events
push

# Container architecture (important for Apple Silicon Macs)
--container-architecture linux/amd64
